@41="Project Image (Illusion)
Level: 10
Range: Visual range of caster
Duration: 2 turns
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: None

This spell creates a quasi-real duplicate of the caster, whilst making himself or herself improved invisible for the duration, he or she cannot act while controlling the image, which is projected to any spot within spell range and receives the full complement of spells its creator had memorized at time of casting, it cannot attack.

The image can be removed by means of a successful dispel magic spell or other means of revealing illusions; the caster can also end it at any time."
@42="Malec-Keth's Flame Fist"
@43="Malec-Keth's Flame Fist (Evocation)
Level: 7
Range: Touch
Duration: 1 round/2 levels
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: Touched creatures
Saving Throw: Special

When this spell is completed, the caster's hand bursts into light and is surrounded by an aura of flame. The caster suffers no damage from this effect.

If the wizard strikes an opponent in melee, the subject must save vs spell. If successful, the flame remains on the caster's hand and the touched creature suffers 2d4 fire damage. If the save is failed, the flame leaves the caster's hand to surround the victim's body in searing fire. The superheated aura burns for 1 round, inflicting 1d4 damage per level of the caster. Only one target per round can be so immolated."